<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hopeless-adj">hopeless <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'həʊpləs/    美 /'hoʊpləs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>没有希望的；绝望的；无可救药的；糟透的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All of a sudden I started to feel rather hopeless.
突然之间，我感到非常绝望。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The lawyers said it was a hopeless case.
律师们说这个案件已无可挽回。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm <strong>hopeless at</strong> maths.
我的数学很差。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>hopelessly /'həʊpləsli/ adv <br />
hopelessness /'həʊpləsnəs/ n   </p></div>